{"type":"message","id":"4c7246f5","parentId":"97addc20","timestamp":"2026-03-17T03:48:26.108Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec:9","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Fetching skill\nakshare-finance  Akshare Finance\nSummary: AKShare财经数据接口库封装，提供股票、期货、期权、基金、外汇、债券、指数、加密货币等金融产品的基本面数据、实时和历史行情数据、衍生数据。\nOwner: BenAngel65\nCreated: 2026-02-27T15:07:49.129Z\nUpdated: 2026-02-27T15:16:54.678Z\nLatest: 1.0.0\nLicense: MIT-0 (Free to use, modify, and redistribute. No attribution required.)\nTags: latest=1.0.0"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1499,"aggregated":"- Fetching skill\nakshare-finance  Akshare Finance\nSummary: AKShare财经数据接口库封装，提供股票、期货、期权、基金、外汇、债券、指数、加密货币等金融产品的基本面数据、实时和历史行情数据、衍生数据。\nOwner: BenAngel65\nCreated: 2026-02-27T15:07:49.129Z\nUpdated: 2026-02-27T15:16:54.678Z\nLatest: 1.0.0\nLicense: MIT-0 (Free to use, modify, and redistribute. No attribution required.)\nTags: latest=1.0.0","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773719306105}}
{"type":"message","id":"493042a6","parentId":"4c7246f5","timestamp":"2026-03-17T03:48:26.447Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec:10","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Fetching skill\nfinance-news-pro  财经新闻深度分析技能\nSummary: 财经新闻深度分析技能。从多个财经源抓取内容，进行情感分析（利好/利空/中性）、影响评估（行业/公司/市场）、关键信息提取，生成专业投资简报。支持 A 股/港股/美股、行业板块、个股分析。\nOwner: SuCriss\nCreated: 2026-03-13T07:40:24.277Z\nUpdated: 2026-03-13T07:51:52.245Z\nLatest: 1.0.1\nLicense: MIT-0 (Free to use, modify, and redistribute. No attribution required.)\nTags: latest=1.0.1"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1833,"aggregated":"- Fetching skill\nfinance-news-pro  财经新闻深度分析技能\nSummary: 财经新闻深度分析技能。从多个财经源抓取内容，进行情感分析（利好/利空/中性）、影响评估（行业/公司/市场）、关键信息提取，生成专业投资简报。支持 A 股/港股/美股、行业板块、个股分析。\nOwner: SuCriss\nCreated: 2026-03-13T07:40:24.277Z\nUpdated: 2026-03-13T07:51:52.245Z\nLatest: 1.0.1\nLicense: MIT-0 (Free to use, modify, and redistribute. No attribution required.)\nTags: latest=1.0.1","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773719306444}}
{"type":"message","id":"66983d69","parentId":"493042a6","timestamp":"2026-03-17T03:48:34.614Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到了几个不错的金融 Skills：\n\n## 📊 金融 Skills 推荐\n\n### 1. **tushare-finance** ⭐ 推荐\n- **功能**：获取中国金融市场数据（A股、港股、美股、基金、期货、债券）\n- **特点**：支持 220+ 个 Tushare Pro 接口，包括股票行情、财务报表、宏观经济指标（GDP/CPI 等）\n- **版本**：2.0.6\n- **适用场景**：股价查询、财务分析、指数行情、宏观数据\n\n### 2. **akshare-finance**\n- **功能**：AKShare 财经数据接口库封装\n- **特点**：覆盖股票、期货、期权、基金、外汇、债券、指数、加密货币等\n- **版本**：1.0.0\n- **适用场景**：多品类金融产品数据获取\n\n### 3. **finance-news-pro** ⭐ 推荐\n- **功能**：财经新闻深度分析\n- **特点**：情感分析（利好/利空/中性）、影响评估、关键信息提取、生成投资简报\n- **版本**：1.0.1\n- **适用场景**：A股/港股/美股、行业板块、个股分析\n\n---\n\n需要我安装哪个？或者您有特定的金融数据需求（比如只看股票价格、或者需要财经新闻分析）？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":563,"output":281,"cacheRead":18688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19532,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773719306447}}
